'''vehicle_breakdowns''' is a variable of Openttd.cfg file:

Sets the frequency which vehicles break down in the game.<br><br>
0 = none (no breakdowns regardless of the condition of the vehicle)<br>
1 = reduced<br>
2 = normal<br>

<pre>
[difficulty]
vehicle_breakdowns = 1
</pre>

'''Valid options:''' [ 0 | 1 | 2 ]

'''Default:''' 1


